you use the comand code to pick up things… for instance ::pickup 1048 1 means that you pick up a white party hat. ::pickup is the command, 1048 is the item id and 1 is the item amount [br][size=1]Posted at: November 24, 2006, 10:15:47 PM[/size][hr]and im not sure about monsters im not a very big fan of hybridscape… i sugest download project 16 and if you want to make your own then download testscape
